This course in criminology offers students ability to relate changes in the dynamics of crime to various criminological theories. This course in criminology gives an overview of different perspectives on crime, different criminological theories and research methods used in criminological studies.Objectives/eesmärkid:  Students will be able to relate changes in the dynamics of crime to various criminological theories. Students will get an overview of different theories of crime. Their understanding about the causes of crime will become more rational.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After passing the course student Students are able to relate changes in the dynamics of crime to various criminological theories. Student has knowledge about different criminological theories and research methods.
